<p class="bibl"><span class="book">Ruskin, Turner and the Storm Cloud</span>. Ed. Suzanne Fagence Cooper and Richard Johns. York: York Art Gallery and Abbott Hall Art Gallery in Association with Paul Holberton Publishing, 2019. [<a href="../../authors/ruskin/reviews/whittingham.html">Review</a> by Selby Whittingham]
</p> 

<p class="bibl"><span class="book">Ruskin, Turner and the Storm Cloud</span>. Ed. Suzanne Fagence Cooper and Richard Johns. York: York Art Gallery and Abbott Hall Art Gallery in Association with Paul Holberton Publishing, 2019. [<a href="../ruskin/york2019.html">Review</a> by George P. Landow]
